        <num>50-5-54</num>
        <content>
          <p>The commissioner of administrative services is authorized and empowered by this part to make all rules, regulations, and stipulations and to provide specifications to carry out the terms and provisions of this part as may be necessary for the purposes of this part. The rules and regulations as prescribed by the commissioner shall be published in pamphlet form and all the departments of the state government shall be furnished with copies of the same.</p>
          <p>(Ga. L. 1939, p. 160, ยง 2.)</p>
